values: This is Leslies Daughter,Tia I'm just letting u know my mother passed away tonight Nov 21st,2006 at 10:32pm EST While my mom was in the hospital she found out she was HIV+ she had a brain infection called toxoplamosis please keep her in your prayers I Love u Mommy Tia my mom was a wonderful poet i always wish i had her talent...remember her www.lyricaltone.com

A part of me really hates the idea of a friends-only journal.

As times change and personal needs change, it is important to be flexible and realistic.

Big Brother is watching.  Will having a friends-only journal stop him from watching? No.

But it will make it just a little bit harder for him to watch...

Paranoia much?  No, not really. I just have my eyes wide open.

"1984" has arrived, ladies and gentlemen.

So...you know the drill...please comment to be added.
